News
• We’ve added sounds to the app. You’ll hear them when sending payments, scanning codes or tapping the confirmation screen.
• Your QR code is now found at the same place as your scanner. Easily accessible with a right swipe on the home screen.

• VoiceOver and Dynamic Type have been fine-tuned.
